{"title":"诗画配","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1983,"month":1,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗画配"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"君子动口不动手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"专磨嘴皮嚼舌头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"消灭鼠患讲运筹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不妨研究再研究。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人主张广畜猫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人强调多养狗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人建议堵墙洞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人鼓吹盖高楼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人赞成下毒药，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人坚持用饵诱……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七嘴八舌主意多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高谈阔论没个够。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从长计议不焦急，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听任耗子满屋走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天长地久有时尽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐而论道几时休？（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}